"""
        Test headers_prettify
        key of dictionary made up of evolver, givenName, quantity
        """
test_dict = {'key1:part1:part2': 'Zed', 'key2:part1:part2': 39,
    'key3:part1:part2': 9}
test_output = odtchomp.headers_prettify(test_dict)
print(test_output)
self.assertEqual(test_output, {'key1 part1 part2': 'Zed',
    'key2 part1 part2': 39, 'key3 part1 part2': 9})
